{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Can geographic information"},{"time":3000,"text":"make you healthy?"},{"time":7000,"text":"In 2001 I got hit by a train."},{"time":11000,"text":"My train was a heart attack."},{"time":14000,"text":"I found myself in a hospital"},{"time":16000,"text":"in an intensive-care ward,"},{"time":18000,"text":"recuperating from emergency surgery."},{"time":21000,"text":"And I suddenly realized something:"},{"time":23000,"text":"that I was completely in the dark."},{"time":26000,"text":"I started asking my questions, \"Well, why me?\""},{"time":28000,"text":"\"Why now?\" \"Why here?\""},{"time":30000,"text":"\"Could my doctor have warned me?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"So, what I want to do here in the few minutes I have with you"},{"time":36000,"text":"is really talk about what is the formula for life and good health."},{"time":41000,"text":"Genetics, lifestyle and environment."},{"time":44000,"text":"That's going to sort of contain our risks,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and if we manage those risks"},{"time":48000,"text":"we're going to live a good life and a good healthy life."},{"time":51000,"text":"Well, I understand the genetics and lifestyle part."},{"time":55000,"text":"And you know why I understand that?"},{"time":57000,"text":"Because my physicians constantly"},{"time":60000,"text":"ask me questions about this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"Have you ever had to fill out those long,"},{"time":64000,"text":"legal-size forms in your doctor's office?"},{"time":67000,"text":"I mean, if you're lucky enough you get to do it more than once, right?"},{"time":70000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":71000,"text":"Do it over and over again. And they ask you questions"},{"time":73000,"text":"about your lifestyle and your family history,"},{"time":76000,"text":"your medication history, your surgical history,"},{"time":80000,"text":"your allergy history ... did I forget any history?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"But this part of the equation I didn't really get,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and I don't think my physicians"},{"time":91000,"text":"really get this part of the equation."},{"time":93000,"text":"What does that mean, my environment?"},{"time":96000,"text":"Well, it can mean a lot of things."},{"time":98000,"text":"This is my life. These are my life places."},{"time":101000,"text":"We all have these."},{"time":103000,"text":"While I'm talking I'd like you to also be thinking about:"},{"time":106000,"text":"How many places have you lived?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"Just think about that, you know, wander through"},{"time":111000,"text":"your life thinking about this."},{"time":113000,"text":"And you realize that you spend it in a variety of different places."},{"time":117000,"text":"You spend it at rest and you spend it at work."},{"time":119000,"text":"And if you're like me, you're in an airplane a good portion of your time"},{"time":122000,"text":"traveling some place."},{"time":124000,"text":"So, it's not really simple"},{"time":126000,"text":"when somebody asks you, \"Where do you live, where do you work,"},{"time":128000,"text":"and where do you spend all your time?"},{"time":130000,"text":"And where do you expose yourselves to risks"},{"time":133000,"text":"that maybe perhaps you don't even see?\""},{"time":137000,"text":"Well, when I have done this on myself,"},{"time":139000,"text":"I always come to the conclusion"},{"time":141000,"text":"that I spend about 75 percent of my time"},{"time":145000,"text":"relatively in a small number of places."},{"time":148000,"text":"And I don't wander far from that place"},{"time":150000,"text":"for a majority of my time,"},{"time":152000,"text":"even though I'm an extensive global trekker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"Now, I'm going to take you on a little journey here."},{"time":159000,"text":"I started off in Scranton, Pennsylvania."},{"time":161000,"text":"I don't know if anybody might hail from northeastern Pennsylvania,"},{"time":164000,"text":"but this is where I spent my first 19 years"},{"time":167000,"text":"with my little young lungs."},{"time":169000,"text":"You know, breathing high concentrations here"},{"time":172000,"text":"of sulfur dioxide, carbon dioxide"},{"time":174000,"text":"and methane gas,"},{"time":176000,"text":"in unequal quantities -- 19 years of this."},{"time":179000,"text":"And if you've been in that part of the country,"},{"time":181000,"text":"this is what those piles of burning, smoldering coal waste look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"So then I decided to leave that part of the world,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and I was going to go to the mid-west."},{"time":191000,"text":"OK, so I ended up in Louisville, Kentucky."},{"time":194000,"text":"Well, I decided to be neighbors to a place called Rubbertown."},{"time":198000,"text":"They manufacture plastics. They use large quantities chloroprene"},{"time":201000,"text":"and benzene."},{"time":203000,"text":"Okay, I spent 25 years, in my middle-age lungs now,"},{"time":208000,"text":"breathing various concentrations of that."},{"time":211000,"text":"And on a clear day it always looked like this, so you never saw it."},{"time":215000,"text":"It was insidious and it was really happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"Then I decided I had to get really smart,"},{"time":220000,"text":"I would take this job in the West Coast."},{"time":223000,"text":"And I moved to Redlands California."},{"time":226000,"text":"Very nice, and there"},{"time":228000,"text":"my older, senior lungs, as I like to call them,"},{"time":232000,"text":"I filled with particulate matter, carbon dioxide and very high doses of ozone."},{"time":238000,"text":"Okay? Almost like the highest in the nation."},{"time":240000,"text":"Alright, this is what it looks like on a good day."},{"time":242000,"text":"If you've been there, you know what I'm talking about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"So, what's wrong with this picture?"},{"time":248000,"text":"Well, the picture is, there is a huge gap here."},{"time":250000,"text":"The one thing that never happens in my doctor's office:"},{"time":254000,"text":"They never ask me about my place history."},{"time":257000,"text":"No doctor, can I remember, ever asking me,"},{"time":260000,"text":"\"Where have you lived?\""},{"time":262000,"text":"They haven't asked me what kind of the quality"},{"time":264000,"text":"of the drinking water that I put in my mouth"},{"time":266000,"text":"or the food that I ingest into my stomach."},{"time":270000,"text":"They really don't do that. It's missing."},{"time":273000,"text":"Look at the kind of data that's available."},{"time":276000,"text":"This data's from all over the world --"},{"time":278000,"text":"countries spend billions of dollars investing in this kind of research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"Now, I've circled the places where I've been."},{"time":285000,"text":"Well, by design, if I wanted to have a heart attack"},{"time":288000,"text":"I'd been in the right places. Right?"},{"time":293000,"text":"So, how many people are in the white?"},{"time":295000,"text":"How many people in the room have spent the majority of their life"},{"time":297000,"text":"in the white space?"},{"time":300000,"text":"Anybody? Boy you're lucky."},{"time":302000,"text":"How many have spent it in the red places?"},{"time":305000,"text":"Oh, not so lucky."},{"time":307000,"text":"There are thousands of these kinds of maps"},{"time":310000,"text":"that are displayed in atlases"},{"time":312000,"text":"all over the world."},{"time":314000,"text":"They give us some sense of what's going"},{"time":316000,"text":"to be our train wreck."},{"time":319000,"text":"But none of that's in my medical record."},{"time":321000,"text":"And it's not in yours either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"So, here's my friend Paul."},{"time":325000,"text":"He's a colleague. He allowed his cell phone to be tracked"},{"time":329000,"text":"every two hours, 24/7,"},{"time":332000,"text":"365 days out of the year"},{"time":334000,"text":"for the last two years, everywhere he went."},{"time":337000,"text":"And you can see he's been to a few places around the United States."},{"time":341000,"text":"And this is where he has spent most of his time."},{"time":345000,"text":"If you really studied that you might have some clues"},{"time":348000,"text":"as to what Paul likes to do."},{"time":351000,"text":"Anybody got any clues? Ski. Right."},{"time":354000,"text":"We can zoom in here, and we suddenly see"},{"time":357000,"text":"that now we see where Paul has really spent a majority of his time."},{"time":361000,"text":"And all of those black dots are all of the"},{"time":365000,"text":"toxic release inventories"},{"time":367000,"text":"that are monitored by the EPA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369000,"text":"Did you know that data existed?"},{"time":372000,"text":"For every community in the United States,"},{"time":374000,"text":"you could have your own personalized map of that."},{"time":378000,"text":"So, our cell phones can now build a place history."},{"time":381000,"text":"This is how Paul did it. He did it with his iPhone."},{"time":384000,"text":"This might be what we end up with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386000,"text":"This is what the physician would have"},{"time":389000,"text":"in front of him and her when we enter that exam room"},{"time":392000,"text":"instead of just the pink slip that said I paid at the counter. Right?"},{"time":396000,"text":"This could be my little assessment."},{"time":398000,"text":"And he looks at that and he says,"},{"time":400000,"text":"\"Whoa Bill,"},{"time":402000,"text":"I suggest that maybe you not decide,"},{"time":405000,"text":"just because you're out here in beautiful California,"},{"time":407000,"text":"and it's warm every day,"},{"time":409000,"text":"that you get out and run at six o'clock at night."},{"time":412000,"text":"I'd suggest that that's a bad idea Bill,"},{"time":415000,"text":"because of this report.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"What I'd like to leave you for are two prescriptions."},{"time":422000,"text":"Okay, number one is, we must teach physicians"},{"time":424000,"text":"about the value of geographical information."},{"time":428000,"text":"It's called geomedicine. There are about a half a dozen programs in the world right now"},{"time":432000,"text":"that are focused on this."},{"time":434000,"text":"And they're in the early stages of development."},{"time":437000,"text":"These programs need to be supported,"},{"time":440000,"text":"and we need to teach our future"},{"time":442000,"text":"doctors of the world"},{"time":444000,"text":"the importance of some of the information"},{"time":446000,"text":"I've shared here with you today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"The second thing we need to do"},{"time":450000,"text":"is while we're spending billions and billions"},{"time":452000,"text":"of dollars all over the world"},{"time":455000,"text":"building an electronic health record,"},{"time":457000,"text":"we make sure we put a place history"},{"time":459000,"text":"inside that medical record."},{"time":462000,"text":"It not only will be important for the physician;"},{"time":465000,"text":"it will be important for the researchers"},{"time":467000,"text":"that now will have huge samples to draw upon."},{"time":471000,"text":"But it will also be useful for us."},{"time":473000,"text":"I could have made the decision, if I had this information,"},{"time":477000,"text":"not to move to the ozone capital"},{"time":480000,"text":"of the United States, couldn't I? I could make that decision."},{"time":483000,"text":"Or I could negotiate with my employer"},{"time":485000,"text":"to make that decision"},{"time":487000,"text":"in the best interest of myself and my company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"With that, I would like to just say that Jack Lord said"},{"time":496000,"text":"this almost 10 years ago."},{"time":499000,"text":"Just look at that for a minute."},{"time":501000,"text":"That was what the conclusion"},{"time":503000,"text":"of the Dartmouth Atlas of Healthcare was about,"},{"time":506000,"text":"was saying that we can explain the geographic variations"},{"time":509000,"text":"that occur in disease, in illness, in wellness,"},{"time":513000,"text":"and how our healthcare system actually operates."},{"time":516000,"text":"That was what he was talking about"},{"time":518000,"text":"on that quote."},{"time":520000,"text":"And I would say he got it right almost a decade ago."},{"time":524000,"text":"So, I'd very much like to see us begin to"},{"time":526000,"text":"really seize this as an opportunity to get this into our medical records."},{"time":530000,"text":"So with that, I'll leave you that"},{"time":532000,"text":"in my particular view of view of health:"},{"time":536000,"text":"Geography always matters."},{"time":538000,"text":"And I believe that geographic information"},{"time":540000,"text":"can make both you and me very healthy. Thank you."},{"time":542000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}